region of the $N_{\\rm H}$-$\\lambda_{\\rm\nEdd}$ plane, and therefore that radiation pressure feedback on the dusty\ninterstellar medium may be driving a phase of blowout that has been ongoing for\na few $10^{5}$ years. The wider properties, including [OIII] narrow-line region\nkinematics, broadly agree with this interpretation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Oct 2019 18:03:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Apr 2020 10:07:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-13"}
